### requires: [gavrasm or AVRA] and [avrdude with osuisp2].
###             gavrasm: http://www.avr-asm-tutorial.net/gavrasm/index_en.html
###				AVRA:	 http://avra.sourceforge.net/
###             osuisp2: http://beaversource.oregonstate.edu/projects/osuisp2/
